          <p class='first-para'>
            I thank the hon. Gentleman for giving way and for securing the debate.</p><p>
            It is not even a question of the Government providing the same amount as last year; they have given less money. Will the hon. Gentleman join us in asking the Government for at least matching revenues to put towards flood defence?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0377P0_20020109_WH_88'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-heath' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
